body.name: 2024 Release WiFi Extender Signal Booster for Home, 6X Faster Longest Range Up to 12000sq.ft, Internet Repeater with Ethernet Port,WiFi Amplifier - 1 Tap Setup
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Tuesday, February 20 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: 【Coverage up to 12000Sq.ft】 The WiFi range extender extend and boost your existing Wi-Fi to hard-to-reach areas, covers up to 12000 sq.ft. Penetrates floors, walls and extending your internet wireless network to every corner of the house, and beyond to the front porch, backyard and garage.
【One touch connection 】- Press the WPS Button on routers then press WPS on Wifi Extender to make fast connection.

【More Zones】Spots in rooms,basement，garage，bedroom， with weak WiFi coverage with our WiFi range extender. Please note :the WiFi repeater only extends WiFi coverage and does not speed up the original router or maintain the same speed as the original router.(When using repeater Mode, the router speed may be reducedas the distance increases)

【High Speed WiFi Extender】The wifi extender booster uses the latest chips to allow wireless signals to reach 300Mbps in the 2.4GHz band. Maximizing your network quality and reduce the loss of data transmission, allowing you to enjoy fast and stable data transmission for video streaming, 4K videos, games at home.

【Easy Set Up & 1-Year Warranty】Use the web browser on your smartphone/tablet /PC for settings. It is easy to set up according to the user manual, without complicated steps and techniques. You can also press the WPS button on the WiFi extender and router at the same time for a fast connection. Edtiske provides you with lifelong technical support and employ a 1-YEAR warranty policy to give you more peace of mind.
body.description: Specifications:❶Product No-Branded❷Frequency Range:2.4~2.4835GHz❸Wireless Standard: IEEE 802.11 b/g/n❹Wireless Security:WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK❺Button :1 Reset Button❻Interface Available: 2*Ethernet portProduct Features:📶Easily connect up to 30 devices📶Wireless broadband access up to 300 Mbps.📶Easily boost your router or neighbour's WiFi signal.📶Easy installation instructions make installation quick and easy.📶Supports repeater and AP modes, supports wireless and wired connectivity.📶Universally compliant with IEEE 802.11n, IEEE 802.11g and IEEE 802.11b standards.📶High penetrability through two walls, reliable data transmission for a large house.📶Easy-to-carry wall design makes installation flexible, saying goodbye to the experience of traveling without WiFi.📶The WiFi extender booster compact size and wall-mounted design facilitate flexible installation and movement, making it very suitable for home / travel / office use.

reviews.reviewText: Me encantaron. Los colores son de buena madera y los tonos súper lindos. Llevo un diario de lectura y me sirven mucho para decorarlo. Excelente compra.
Cores lindas e vibrantes material de super qualidade muito bom e bonito compraria novamente, podem comprar sem medo simplesmente incrivel.

reviews.reviewTitle: Colores bonitos pero dificultad para colorear con ellos.
reviews.reviewText: Estos colores pastel son bonitos, es decir que las tonalidades son agradables y suaves, pero hay que tener en cuenta que lo que reseñan otras opiniones es cierto en cuanto a que cuesta trabajo que el color pinte firmemente en tus hojas por lo que hay que presionar fuerte el lápiz y pintar enérgicamente para que el color quede bien. Para nuestro caso están bien porque simplemente los usamos para pintar los días en curso de un calendario así que no necesitamos ni gran definición ni calidad del color. Algo que si nos parece positivo resaltar es que la punta de color es resistente y no se rompe fácilmente a pesar de lo fuerte que tienes que pintar para que el color aparezca.

reviews.reviewerName: Chegou antes do prazo, em madeira de ótima qualidade tamanho ideal. Podem comprar sem medo.
